data.title: WVAH TV 11
data.meta_description:
1 review of WVAH TV 11 "You once held the title as my favorite television channel. Yet now with the over exposure of one certian commercial I have entertain the thought of beginning a boycott. This repetitive run of this advertisement has driven me to stop both WCHS &FOX11.  
    I am a devoted customer of this fast food chain and is always my first choice , but with this my subconscious is turning to avoid avoid Arby's completely! 
   And if given the chance to guess , and I'm positive I'm not the only one. 
Please for the sake of not only mine but the sanity of countless others that have had their limit of Arbys rib sandwich commercial!!  How bout it's restructured to file 13.
Truthfully Johnnie R Harper jr"
